thread.title: Joseph

author: Joseph
title: Joseph
text: Could not have asked for a better experience for a first time tree purchase. The website was easy to explore and understand. All pertinent and relevant information was available. When I received my cherry blossom it was well packaged and protected. Following the easy included planting guide my family and I are already enjoying a blossoming tree. Thank you I look forward to my next order.
